Jane April Pelt and Robert A. Berman, both of Brookline, Mass., plan to he married May 29 in New York, where their engagement has been announced by Mr. and Mrs. Charles Feit of Searingtown, LI., parents of the bride‐to‐be. Her fiancé is the son of Mr. and Mrs. Peter Berman of Maywood, N.J.

Miss Felt, who graduated this year from Boston University, is with Cincinnati‐Edwards Systems Sales in Boston, where her fiance is an advertising coordinator for the Morse Shoe Company. He also is film critic for Nightfall, a monthly magazine on entertainment in New England.

Mr. Feit Is executive vice president of Weight Watchers International. The prospective bridegroom's father is with Unsworth & Co., freight forwarders.